    "gut_harmony_feature_AEPXCy": {
      "type": "gut-harmony-feature",
      "name": "Gut Harmony Feature",
      "settings": {
        "use_theme_colors": false,
        "padding_top": 80,
        "padding_bottom": 80,
        "padding_top_mobile": 40,
        "padding_bottom_mobile": 28,
        "title_gap": 24,
        "column_gap": 24,
        "content_gap": 24,
        "background_color": "#ffffff",
        "title": "The Hidden Shift Most Women Don’t See Coming",
        "title_size": 40,
        "title_size_mobile": 26,
        "title_color": "#3b3b3b",
        "image": "shopify://shop_images/4471191.webp",
        "image_border_radius": 0,
        "body_text": "<p>After 45, your body can begin to process energy differently.</p><p>😬 Meals that used to feel satisfying may now leave you tired.</p><p>🍫 Cravings may feel harder to control.</p><p>💤 Energy may dip earlier in the day.</p><p>And when <strong>your body</strong> is constantly trying to <strong>manage unstable energy, digestion, appetite, and metabolic changes</strong>, it can affect more than your routine.</p><p>It can <strong>affect how present, confident, and connected you feel.</strong></p>",
        "text_size": 16,
        "text_color": "#333333",
        "testimonial_text": "<p><strong>❌ Because desire doesn’t exist in isolation.</strong></p><p><strong>✅ It depends on how your whole body feels.</strong></p>",
        "testimonial_size": 18,
        "testimonial_paragraph_spacing": 12,
        "testimonial_color": "#a9617a",
        "button_text": "",
        "button_link": "",
        "button_show_arrow": true,
